Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.88,0:22:22.88,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.21,0:22:25.73,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.59,0:22:29.30,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}话说 妮娜好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.75,0:22:30.92,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs47\an9\blur2\bord2.5}我说 也帮我介绍一个贵族恩客吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.92,0:22:31.40,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs47\an9\blur2\bord2.5}啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.40,0:22:32.21,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs47\an9\blur2\bord2.5}我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.21,0:22:32.66,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs47\an9\blur2\bord2.5}啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.66,0:22:35.24,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs47\an9\blur2\bord2.5}可以的话 要比你还有钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.56,0:22:38.30,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不后悔吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.14,0:22:39.80,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.14,0:22:43.65,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}现在我回去的话 肯定就走不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.48,0:22:46.15,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对不起 露加姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.94,0:22:49.16,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在最后一刻也要你担心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.23,0:22:52.57,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我要跟约阿希姆走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.16,0:22:56.79,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我很喜欢大伙以及露加姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.79,0:22:59.75,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可若跟你们待在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.37,0:23:02.96,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}总有一天又会憎恨起露加姐你来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.92,0:23:05.50,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而后便会憎恨自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.88,0:23:10.59,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只因为你的坚强 便会伤害到他人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.28,0:23:13.96,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只因为自己的软弱 便会憎恨他人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.93,0:23:18.68,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想跟这个同样软弱 背负同样罪孽之人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.43,0:23:20.95,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}携手同行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.77,0:23:23.90,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因为跟他在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.11,0:23:30.86,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感觉我们都会变得坚强和体贴一点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.82,0:23:33.88,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.91,0:23:37.99,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这孩子 真是让人操尽了心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.89,0:00:04.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,为何可以做到如此地步
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.06,0:00:06.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在如此绝望的...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.65,0:00:09.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,任谁都只能寻找某种依赖的情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.03,0:00:13.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,为何他能理所当然地说出「要活下去」这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:17.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那些东西见了太阳便会消失或者力量减弱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.08,0:00:20.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,胜负关键在于能否撑到天亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:22.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要活下去!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.68,0:00:24.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,为何这个男人的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:26.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是如此掷地有声
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.38,0:00:28.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在我心中回荡
Comment: 0,0:02:09.98,0:02:11.98,DefaultSub,,0,0,0,,/--------START---------/
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.20,0:02:13.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是折断了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.95,0:02:20.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,必须逃离这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:24.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:29.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:31.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:36.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,人?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:40.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托 我走不动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:41.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,帮帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.56,0:02:53.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,千钧一发啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:55.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,简直跟疯牛失控一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:02:58.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:03:00.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.47,0:03:01.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,露加姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:03.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我在下面看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.15,0:03:06.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子艾伦他们都平安无事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:08.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,露加姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.95,0:03:11.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 喂 没时间伤感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:18.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,能走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:19.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.17,0:03:21.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但跑就不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:23.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.38,0:03:27.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:30.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,无论发生什么事都不要露头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.68,0:03:32.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,露加姐姐你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:34.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我会自己想办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:36.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我一个人会害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:39.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:40.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:44.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我要露加姐姐陪着我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:47.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这个桶藏不了两个人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:49.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,再说那样的话谁来封盖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.49,0:03:50.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:54.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是胆小如鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:56.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,露加姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:04:00.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此 倒不如让人见识你是如何地贪生怕死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.88,0:04:02.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,屏住气息不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.23,0:04:04.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不要弄出声音来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.38,0:04:07.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定你这种贪生怕死之人 最能顽强地幸存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:12.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,完工
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:23.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,露加姐姐 露加姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:35.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉自那天之后 自己就迷失在黑夜中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:37.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:41.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是太阳升起的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:45.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,终于到了拔此秘剑的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:47.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,仅此一点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:50.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就比那个时候要好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:05:01.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 再怎么烧也烧不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:02.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,源源不绝地涌过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:13.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,接招! 火焰爆裂丸!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:16.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.18,0:05:18.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,咦你妹啊 你个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:19.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,宰了你信不信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.58,0:05:22.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 这些都是什么东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:26.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是此地死于瘟疫和拷问之人的怨念
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:29.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,它们吸收被吞噬之人的意念后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:30.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,愈发庞大了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:33.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,充满了渴望得救的心愿和怨念
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:37.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,若心有怨念便变成这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:39.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,世间早已淹没在痰盂中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:43.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,为何只有阿尔比安发生这种怪事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:45.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.87,0:05:52.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:54.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不能有这种事情发生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:05:57.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,跟那时候一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:05:59.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛置身噩梦之中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:02.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这真的是现实吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.62,0:06:18.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,若不想死 你自己也动动手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.64,0:06:20.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法尔纳塞大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:25.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在这毛骨悚然的噩梦中站出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:27.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,并毫不退缩...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:29.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...唯一真实的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:32.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 背后也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:35.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法尔纳塞大人 请站在我背后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:37.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,神...神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:38.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,别祈祷!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.75,0:06:40.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那样手就空不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:42.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你握着的是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:52.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.15,0:07:01.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:04.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了 我要崩溃了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.11,0:07:07.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要死了要死了 我要死了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:09.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了了 放我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:10.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,放我离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:14.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,竟在这种时候...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:19.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,明明反正都要死...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:24.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.79,0:07:26.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,血还是热的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:29.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,结局尚未可知啊 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.75,0:07:32.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,越是害怕 就越真切地感受到自己还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:37.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,越是吐血 便越是感受到那腔热血
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:39.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,豁出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.77,0:07:41.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我要求生 露加姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:45.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕 代表着求生的欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:05.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:34.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好壮观
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:37.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,生灵 亡魂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.21,0:08:39.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,此地的所有灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.18,0:08:41.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,正在呼唤同样的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:49.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,此刻 我的世界全体一条心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:52.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,为我而鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:56.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,为渴求我所创造的世界而鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:09:01.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一切皆化为同一个声音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:08.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,它们在讴歌!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:11.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯 那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:18.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,它 它在和那个声音共鸣!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:22.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:23.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.37,0:09:25.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这个剧痛...!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:53.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 光芒...四射
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:12.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格里菲斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:16.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在燃起熊熊火柱的...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.97,0:10:19.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...盲目群羊所聚集的圣地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:21.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,天崩之时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.80,0:10:23.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他将降临
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:05.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是一片惨象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:08.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,塔和怪物都在一夜之间消失得无影无踪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:10.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是不是在做梦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:32.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我还活着...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.33,0:11:34.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,蓬蓬头姐姐 原来你没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:37.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:38.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:40.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 露加姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:43.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.79,0:11:46.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,露加姐姐...去找露加姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.40,0:11:48.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:51.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,露加姐姐...把我塞进桶里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:53.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,之后她怎么样我就不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:55.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,露加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.20,0:11:56.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,露加姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.45,0:11:57.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:11:59.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,露加姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.14,0:12:02.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 在这瓦砾中怎么找她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.31,0:12:04.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:06.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能死 露加姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:13.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这里...我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.74,0:12:14.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是在井下面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.18,0:12:20.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,快拉我上去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.10,0:12:24.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,快要冻僵了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.23,0:12:25.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,露加姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:31.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,呜啊啊 好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.73,0:12:34.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.48,0:12:39.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真的...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:40.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...很暖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.12,0:12:43.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,没白活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:56.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是库夏人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:12:58.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会出现在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.71,0:13:00.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是上次那些斥候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:08.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,上次那个黑衣战士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:10.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,难道就是他?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:11.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:13.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 正如神谕所言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.81,0:13:15.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,此地发生了异变
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.38,0:13:16.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他们也出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.27,0:13:20.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要找的人恐怕就在其中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:22.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:24.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,都走到了这一步
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:26.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,还活不下去就是老天骗人 大骗子!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:28.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,将这些人悉数拿下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:31.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,伤了他们一点也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:33.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是背着大剑那个男子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.11,0:13:34.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不必手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:36.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在砍下他手脚之前不可掉以轻心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:45.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,死!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.88,0:13:46.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,送你归西!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:49.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,个人感情暂且不论
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.93,0:13:50.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:54.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,没有什么比与你并肩作战更振奋人心的了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.77,0:13:57.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,话虽如此 感觉是杯水车薪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.22,0:13:58.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你就吹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:01.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,别动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:03.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,敢动一下这些女人就...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:03.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.19,0:14:07.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,竟拿女人当人质
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.32,0:14:08.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是蛮夷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.09,0:14:13.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些异教徒 在我等圣地意欲何为
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.17,0:14:13.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,艾桑!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.87,0:14:15.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是倔脾气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:18.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法尔纳塞大人 您没事真是万幸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.12,0:14:20.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,副团长 你是怎么脱险的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:22.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等下再详谈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.55,0:14:26.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在我稍微离开期间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.38,0:14:28.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,事情变得有些微妙了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.05,0:14:33.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.75,0:14:37.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.63,0:14:38.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,又来?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:44.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,魔...魔兽?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:50.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是...昨晚噩梦的延续吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:55.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,现在发生什么我都不会吃惊了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:14:56.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,左德!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.83,0:14:57.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,为何会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:04.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这...真是太骇人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:07.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,别感慨了 要逃赶紧逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.08,0:15:10.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 全体别走散
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.78,0:15:12.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一口气突围
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:40.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在那一瞬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.51,0:15:44.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人都屏住了呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.00,0:15:46.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,目光不约而同聚于一处
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.25,0:15:48.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格里...菲斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:05.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,而后觉察到...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:08.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...追求的「希望」已降临
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:20.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,全军 将他拿下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:23.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 施拉特大人...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:24.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,别慌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:28.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这个任务关乎我们巴基拉卡一族的复兴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:30.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你们忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:34.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我族流放国外不下数百年的悲惨历史
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:36.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,此刻正是千载良机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.10,0:16:39.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在大部队到来之前拿下他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.64,0:16:40.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,上!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.11,0:16:50.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好极了 这边人少了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:52.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法尔纳塞大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:56.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个 在磨蹭啥呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.88,0:17:17.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伦和剑士先生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.01,0:17:19.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,难道还在那...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.57,0:17:22.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,站住 你还没吃够苦头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.38,0:17:24.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要你管 小喽啰让开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.38,0:17:25.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么?! 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.86,0:17:38.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,库夏大部队也来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:41.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他们没发现我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.93,0:17:44.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎能这样 你们要抛下他们两个吗!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:46.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是迫不得已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:47.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这次真的会死人的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:49.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,畜生!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.46,0:17:54.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:11.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他是何方神圣...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.57,0:18:18.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,非人之物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:20.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一而再再而三
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:22.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这次又是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.44,0:18:29.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他们没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.05,0:18:32.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 跟如此大军为敌...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:36.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题 他肯定能保护好艾伦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.96,0:18:39.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿 可别褂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:42.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会去讨回你欠我的人情的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.49,0:18:44.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,傻逼 别嚷嚷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:55.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 除了我们还有人活下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.52,0:18:58.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,逃进塔的都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:19:02.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一溜烟地逃离塔的不信神者都活了下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.62,0:19:07.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,想必他们再也不想祈祷了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.75,0:19:09.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,并非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:14.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,求生和逃离恐惧是两回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.74,0:19:16.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不随波逐流
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.21,0:19:19.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,为了最终生还而挣扎求存之人才会幸存下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.25,0:19:24.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道神在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.76,0:19:30.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但还是为人类留下了自己想办法解决的领域
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.89,0:19:32.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,露加姐姐 那是?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.65,0:19:33.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这些花?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:36.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,献给死在蛋中的雏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.35,0:19:37.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.28,0:19:40.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,没等孵出来就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:42.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不曾见过任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:44.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,也不为人所知
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:46.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有那么一个寂寞的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:49.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沉眠在那瓦砾之下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:52.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想用这朵花为其饯别
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:55.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不管它生前有着何等罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:19:57.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,至少死后不用孤零零的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:20:02.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 若它的愿望实现了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.13,0:20:05.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,今后 世界将会迎来怎样的...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:08.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那么有缘再会了 各位姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.53,0:20:11.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就此告辞 再见!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.30,0:20:13.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,为了答谢你 我提供免费服务
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.77,0:20:18.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我要赶路啊 先记着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.65,0:20:21.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是行色匆匆的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.07,0:20:23.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,总算松了口气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:26.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道艾伦怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.07,0:20:29.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有那位黑色剑士保护 肯定没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:32.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他对着摩兹古斯都毫无退缩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:37.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 保护一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:40.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,跟陪伴一个人大不一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:45.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我去解下手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:46.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:47.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.93,0:20:52.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.73,0:20:57.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,约阿希姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:20:59.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.65,0:21:04.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我想跟你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:09.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候我...觉得你...很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.62,0:21:13.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,想着不去告发便会被你们杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.58,0:21:16.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然事到如今已难以敌口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.87,0:21:19.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,其实...我对你...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.92,0:21:21.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前很想和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.84,0:21:24.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 我没有勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.38,0:21:26.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,自己放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.09,0:21:28.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:31.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:32.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.10,0:21:33.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.23,0:21:42.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎...怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.86,0:21:46.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我...要追上黑色剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:47.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:50.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我要弃僧籍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.51,0:21:54.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,告辞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:59.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底没能逃离童年阴影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.21,0:22:01.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,然后它...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.86,0:22:05.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,终于成形 出现在我眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.52,0:22:11.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,简直像是那个懦弱的我命中注定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.46,0:22:14.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,为立于黑暗中的唯一一人...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.72,0:22:18.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...黑色剑士所引领
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.27,0:23:43.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,从那天在边境产生龟裂开始
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.85,0:23:46.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,世界的形态便开始崩溃
